# Architecture pointer

- Use `docs/architecture.md` as the canonical source for:
  - Repo layout and ownership boundaries
  - Routing/rewrite topology and precedence
  - Build and deploy flow
  - Common change playbooks and invariants
- When planning or implementing multi-file changes, check that file first.
- If code and docs diverge, update `docs/architecture.md` in the same change.
- For cross-repo context (repo purposes, relationships, shared infra), read `../haderach-tasks/repos.md`.
